quran[4{c,v,t}:
5,42,( yeh ) jhooti baatein bananay ke jasoosi karne walay aur ( rishwat ka ) haraam maal khanay walay hain agar yeh tumahray paas ( koi muqadma Faisal karanay ko ) ayen to tum un mein faisla kar dena ya aaraaz karna aur agar un se aaraaz karo ge to woh tumhara kuch bhi nahi bigaar saken ge aur agar faisla karna chaho to insaaf ka faisla karna ke khuda insaaf karne walon ko dost rakhta hai
5,43,aur yeh tum se ( apne muqadmaat ) kionkar Faisal krayn ge jabkay khud un ke paas torat ( mojood ) hai jis mein khuda ka hukum ( likha howa ) hai ( yeh usay jantay hain ) phir is ke baad is se phir jatay hain aur yeh log imaan hi nahi rakhtay
5,44,bay shak hum ne torait nazil farmai jis mein hadaayat aur roshni hai isi ke mutabiq anbia jo ( khuda ke ) farmanbardar they yahudion ko hukum dete rahay hain aur mashaiykh aur ulama bhi kyunkay woh kitaab khuda ke nigehbaan muqarrar kiye gay they aur is par gawah they ( yani hukum Ellahi ka yaqeen rakhtay they ) to tum logon se mat darna aur mujhi se drtay rehna aur meri ayaton ke badlay thori si qeemat nah lena aur jo khuda ke nazil farmaiye hue ehkaam ke mutabiq hukum nah day to aisay hi log kafir hain
5,45,aur hum ne un logon ke liye torat mein yeh hukum likh diya tha ke jaan ke badlay jaan aur aankhh ke badlay aankhh aur naak ke badlay naak aur kaan ke badlay kaan aur daant ke badlay daant aur sab zakhamo ka isi terhan badla hai lekin jo shakhs badla maaf kar day woh is ke liye kaffara hoga aur jo khuda ke nazil farmaiye hue ehkaam ke mutabiq hukum nah day to aisay hi log be insaaf hain
